history.content: We’re conducting a paid ($50) study to better understand how users attempt to create fairness-aware machine learning models that identify and mitigate potential biases in a real-world setting through the utilization of fair-ml toolkits (such as Fairlearn and AIF360).  See the form linked here for more information and to sign up if you are interested in participating this week! Thanks!
